 1)Create a table for students which should contain the following columns
    id, name, subject,mark,course
    Write subquery which should return student details whose mark should be grater than average.

 2) Write a multi row subquery which should contain students with marks > 50

use sla;
create table students (
	std_id int,
    std_name varchar(20) not null,
    subject_name varchar(20) ,
    sub_mark float,
    course varchar(20) 
);

insert into students 
